I'm so happy.

637
00:45:46,350 --> 00:45:49,360
Uh... so what does your family do?

638
00:45:49,640 --> 00:45:51,400
Dad, what kind of question is that?

639
00:45:53,280 --> 00:45:54,280
It's fine.

640
00:45:55,160 --> 00:45:57,080
My family's in the export business.

641
00:45:57,760 --> 00:45:59,080
Oh, really.

642
00:46:01,000 --> 00:46:04,640
Hey, let me ask.
When did you realize you liked guys?

643
00:46:08,820 --> 00:46:10,120
When you're near him,

644
00:46:10,140 --> 00:46:12,910
your heart just goes
really pounding?

645
00:46:13,570 --> 00:46:16,360
Snow, that question is out of line.

646
00:46:16,700 --> 00:46:18,720
How? It's perfectly normal.

647
00:46:18,880 --> 00:46:22,710
Okay, that's enough.
Is that even appropriate?

648
00:46:24,200 --> 00:46:27,680
It's fine.
Ask me anything you want.

649
00:46:31,350 --> 00:46:32,350
- Mom.
- Hmm?

650
00:46:32,370 --> 00:46:34,919
Have Phi Save and Phi Guy go live.

651
00:46:34,920 --> 00:46:37,280
Trust me.
They'll sell out in minutes.

652
00:46:41,640 --> 00:46:43,400
