653
00:46:46,800 --> 00:46:50,600
Any ladies interested in some
really good Thai desserts?

654
00:46:50,880 --> 00:46:53,800
That's right.
Try these, and you'll be amazed.

655
00:46:54,700 --> 00:46:56,090
Hey, they gave us a gift.

656
00:46:56,110 --> 00:46:57,110
Hey.

657
00:46:57,270 --> 00:46:59,520
Thank you so much. Thank you.

658
00:46:59,550 --> 00:47:02,840
