661
00:47:09,370 --> 00:47:10,760
- Mmm.
- Good? Is it good?

662
00:47:11,680 --> 00:47:15,140
Mmm. It's so soft and chewy.

663
00:47:15,400 --> 00:47:16,970
Just melts in your mouth.

664
00:47:17,390 --> 00:47:18,390
Hmm.

665
00:47:19,370 --> 00:47:20,230
Hmm.

666
00:47:20,250 --> 00:47:22,799
"You were holding hands, crossing
the street at Siam, right?"

667
00:47:22,800 --> 00:47:26,800
"Squee... delightful.
Are you two together?"

668
00:47:26,920 --> 00:47:29,960
"Running a business together too.
The cutest thing."

669
00:47:29,990 --> 00:47:31,840
"Share a bite nice and close."

670
00:47:32,660 --> 00:47:34,240
Share a bite nice and close?

671
00:47:34,470 --> 00:47:36,540
Mmm, have a heart.

672
00:47:36,560 --> 00:47:38,520
"If you do it, I'll buy ten boxes."

673
00:47:38,920 --> 00:47:40,760
Ten boxes if we do it?

674
00:48:09,130 --> 00:48:12,440
- Aaah.
- Aaah.

675
00:48:18,500 --> 00:48:21,319
Mmm, it really is soft and chewy.

676
00:48:21,320 --> 00:48:22,680
Right?

677
00:48:24,180 --> 00:48:25,320
We've just sold ten boxes.

678
00:48:25,340 --> 00:48:26,700
Thank you so much.

679
00:48:26,720 --> 00:48:28,030
- Phi Sorn.
- Thank you so much.

680
00:48:28,640 --> 00:48:32,560
Phi Sorn, look.
Sales are almost at two thousand.

681
00:48:55,460 --> 00:48:57,040
Total sales, fifteen thousand.

682
00:48:59,960 --> 00:49:04,829
