694
00:49:43,410 --> 00:49:44,280
Hmm.

695
00:49:44,281 --> 00:49:45,720
Yes, Father.

696
00:49:46,940 --> 00:49:47,940
Heh.

697
00:49:55,000 --> 00:49:56,600
So how was it?

698
00:49:56,900 --> 00:49:57,900
Really fun.

699
00:49:58,270 --> 00:50:00,840
